                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The agent critically hits a creature that they've identified with @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Recall Knowledge]</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The agent Steps or Strides. This movement doesn't trigger reactions from the triggering creature.</p>"
