                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The agent Recalls Knowledge about a creature they can see. On a success, the subject is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Off-Guard] to the agent until the end of the agent's next turn (or for 1 minute on a critical success).</p>"
